   {
      "body" : "I'll defer to y'all to work this out; listening only for connections from localhost sounds interesting, although I'll just say I've regretted having subtle interactions between command-line arguments in the past and good documentation might be the best answer (either tell p2pool users to use -connect=... -listen=1  or tell others to use -connect=... -listen=0 ).\r\n",
      "created_at" : "2012-03-06T14:17:11Z",
      "html_url" : "https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/914#issuecomment-4344968",
